---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = 'Terms of Use — Genfy';
const description = 'Terms and conditions for using the Genfy site and its online generators.';
---
<Layout title={title} description={description} lang="en">
  <article>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: April 26, 2026.</p>

    <h2>1. Acceptance</h2>
    <p>
      By accessing genfy.net you accept these terms. If you do not agree, please do not
      use the site.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Permitted use</h2>
    <p>
      Genfy offers free, signup-free online generators. You may use the results
      (passwords, names, QR codes, text) for personal or commercial purposes, with no
      mandatory attribution.
    </p>
    <p>Not allowed:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Massive or automated scraping of the site without authorization.</li>
      <li>Reusing the site's code or copying it under another brand.</li>
      <li>Using Genfy to generate illegal, fraudulent or rights-infringing content.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. No warranties</h2>
    <p>
      Genfy is provided "as is". We don't guarantee results are suitable for every use.
      For example: a generated password is statistically strong, but final security depends
      on the context (length required by the system, secure storage, etc.). Brand name
      ideas may already be registered: check availability before using them.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      We are not liable for direct or indirect damages arising from the use of the site or
      the generated results.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>
      The design, the "Genfy" brand and the site's code are owned by their authors. The
      generated outputs (lorem ipsum text, passwords, name lists) are not copyrighted by
      their generative nature, and you may use them freely.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      The site is sustained by third-party advertising (Google AdSense). Products and
      services advertised are not endorsed by Genfy.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may modify these terms at any time. The last update date is at the top.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Governing law</h2>
    <p>
      These terms are governed by the laws of Argentina, without prejudice to any
      mandatory rules applicable to the user's place of residence.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
